world, of which she has had such bright dreams. How fairy-like does everything a
ppear to her enchanted vision! Each new scene is more charming than the last. Bu
t after a while she finds that beneath this goodly exterior, all is vanity:-207-
the flattery which once charmed her soul, now grates harshly upon her ear; the b
