k-haired young lady, who paused an impressive moment, assumed a tragic expressio
n, and began to read in a measured, solemn tone:A VISIONDark and tempestuous was
 night. Around the throne on high not a single star quivered; but the deep inton
ations of the heavy thunder constantly vibrated upon the ear; whilst the terrifi
