That's all.''Thank you,' said Alice, 'it's very interesting. I never knew so muc
h about a whiting before.''I can tell you more than that, if you like,' said the
 Gryphon. 'Do you know why it's called a whiting?''I never thought about it,' sa
id Alice. 'Why?''IT DOES THE BOOTS AND SHOES.' the Gryphon replied very solemnly
.Alice was thoroughly puzzled. 'Does the boots and shoes!' she repeated in a won
