Call the next witness!' said the King.The next witness was the Duchess's cook. S
he carried the pepper-box in her hand, and Alice guessed who it was, even before
 she got into the court, by the way the people near the door began sneezing all 
at once.'Give your evidence,' said the King.'Shan't,' said the cook.The King loo
